title: UPC CDS I 2026 Apply Online
description: UPSC CDS Examination (I), 2026 : Apply Online Post Update : 11 – 12-2025 Short Description: The UPSC Combined Defence Services (CDS) Examination (I), 2026 is conducted by the Union Public Service Commission for recruitment into IMA, INA, AFA, and OTA. The online application process starts on 10 December 2025, and the last date to apply is 30 December 2025. The examination will be held on 12 April 2026. It is meant for graduate candidates seeking a commissioned officer’s rank in the Indian Arm...
